ROOT_CAUSE: Gate 3 checks `selected_nodes == []` (retrieval found nothing). It does not check
            whether synthesis produced a useful answer. `has_evidence` reflects retrieval success,
            not synthesis success. A topically adjacent but answer-irrelevant chunk passes Gate 3.
